    Note over Test,S3: Flow 1: Distributed Training with PyTorchJob

    Test->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob + LocalQueue<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    Test->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterQueue + ResourceFlavor<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload admission request
    Kueue->>CQ: Check quota & admit workload
    CQ-->>Kueue: Workload admitted
    K8sAPI->>TrainOp: PyTorchJob reconciliation
    TrainOp->>Pods: Create master + worker pods
    Pods->>S3: Download training data<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>Pods: Training data/model artifacts
    Pods->>NCCL: Multi-GPU communication<br/>Dynamic ports, plaintext
    NCCL-->>Pods: Gradient synchronization
    Pods->>S3: Upload model checkpoints<br/>AWS IAM credentials
    Pods-->>K8sAPI: Job completion status
    K8sAPI-->>Test: PyTorchJob status: Succeeded

    Note over Test,S3: Flow 2: Ray Job Submission

    Test->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster + RayJob<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI->>RayHead: RayCluster created
    Test->>RayHead: POST /api/jobs/<br/>HTTP 8265, plaintext, no auth
    RayHead->>RayWorkers: Distribute tasks<br/>TCP 6379, plaintext
    RayWorkers->>S3: Download/upload data<br/>HTTPS 443, AWS IAM
    S3-->>RayWorkers: Data artifacts
    RayWorkers-->>RayHead: Task results
    Test->>RayHead: GET /api/jobs/{jobId}<br/>HTTP 8265, plaintext
    RayHead-->>Test: Job status + results

    Note over Test,S3: Flow 3: Trainer v2 TrainJob with Kueue

    Test->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob + ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>Bearer Token Auth
    K8sAPI->>TrainerV2: TrainJob reconciliation
    TrainerV2->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet
    K8sAPI->>Kueue: Workload admission
    Kueue->>CQ: Quota check & admission
    CQ-->>Kueue: Admitted
    K8sAPI->>Pods: Create training pods from JobSet
    Pods->>S3: Download/upload training artifacts<br/>HTTPS 443, AWS IAM
    S3-->>Pods: Model artifacts
    Pods-->>K8sAPI: TrainJob completion
    K8sAPI-->>Test: TrainJob status: Succeeded
